3b87eb5c-f13f-4b5f-8085-3319513a2955.title: <player>
3b87eb5c-f13f-4b5f-8085-3319513a2955.text:
Not bad, thank you.
What are you building here?

83bf4c00-1a86-442b-8a24-7de1319d4367.title: Bonafido
83bf4c00-1a86-442b-8a24-7de1319d4367.text: Nowt at moment. We're on strike!

0c9e170d-46df-453a-b9d7-5b8f7ca8f1cb.title: Bonafido
0c9e170d-46df-453a-b9d7-5b8f7ca8f1cb.text:
Those strange alchemists are up ta somefin', best go ta
one ov 'em.

2282c901-d8b7-431f-a53d-d0c8b2bb5936.title: <player>
2282c901-d8b7-431f-a53d-d0c8b2bb5936.text: Are you Bonafido by any chance?

a7ab6610-8971-4182-b33b-3c1f1ffe3dde.title: Bonafido
a7ab6610-8971-4182-b33b-3c1f1ffe3dde.text:
That I am.
How can I be of assistance?

a963dc87-eb43-4624-9917-56a39c19ff85.title: <player>
a963dc87-eb43-4624-9917-56a39c19ff85.text:
Well, I've just spoken with Effigy about this tower. He
tells me he hired you to work but you're on strike.
Something about an extended tea break?

d7d309a0-6607-4f2c-a373-ed297e0f9caa.title: Bonafido
d7d309a0-6607-4f2c-a373-ed297e0f9caa.text:
Extended cup o' char? E's tellin' porkies! We know
those alchemi-whatsits are up ta somefin' weird in
building this tower, wot wiv all the machinery, and until
we get some answers we're not movin a muscle.

669a466f-4ac4-4646-ab7e-abc1018b5ef7.title: <player>
669a466f-4ac4-4646-ab7e-abc1018b5ef7.text:
Well, he wanted me to do something about it. Is there
no way I can convince you to continue?

0b3d2e29-97ac-4adb-b6d0-b30f7f6419eb.title: <player>
0b3d2e29-97ac-4adb-b6d0-b30f7f6419eb.text: Well, can I at least have a look inside the tower?

bf94c1a9-3666-4a9a-a69e-5b59a0c202ec.title: Bonafido
bf94c1a9-3666-4a9a-a69e-5b59a0c202ec.text:
Only builders are allowed in there, like. You don't look
much ov a builder to me.

bc7342b3-1f3e-4ac4-af14-36e44a4fa39c.title: <player>
bc7342b3-1f3e-4ac4-af14-36e44a4fa39c.text:
I take offence at that! Give me a chance; you may be
surprised.

065229d4-d5c9-4c01-9d7a-7d411d0b7e6b.title: Bonafido
065229d4-d5c9-4c01-9d7a-7d411d0b7e6b.text:
Okay. Come to me kitted out like a builder - hard hat,
some boots, scruffy trousers and shirt - and I'll let ya
try out ta be one ov us.

d9deabff-21b6-47d2-872c-84cb36f5e9bd.title: Bonafido
d9deabff-21b6-47d2-872c-84cb36f5e9bd.text: Well, if it ain't the wannabe builder!

ba273afd-0006-41c2-8a05-b1ca9b4de427.title: Bonafido
ba273afd-0006-41c2-8a05-b1ca9b4de427.text:
Ya don't seem to be able ta remember anyfin'... Dearie
me.

a78f86b2-9bec-4538-882e-cec4163f87c2.title: Bonafido
a78f86b2-9bec-4538-882e-cec4163f87c2.text:
Come back to me wearin' a hard hat, some scruffy
trousers, a good top and some hard boots. Yow shud
fand some around 'ere.

960673f7-dc5f-464f-a415-2434057a57f4.title: Bonafido
960673f7-dc5f-464f-a415-2434057a57f4.text:
Like a builder frew and frew!
Good job - now it's time to test your skills.

4877f2f3-775a-46ef-a70b-f897372c2564.title: <player>
4877f2f3-775a-46ef-a70b-f897372c2564.text: Okay, what do you want me to build?

e74d1fb0-8e91-4513-923d-ef5bb2987745.title: Bonafido
e74d1fb0-8e91-4513-923d-ef5bb2987745.text:
Build?
Hahaha, don't be a plonka!

fd44b754-a66a-4ead-b784-7e7188e91201.title: Bonafido
fd44b754-a66a-4ead-b784-7e7188e91201.text:
It's not building skills that makes a true builder, you
have to have the right mental attitude, yeah?

5a9ff2cd-84d6-41c5-bf6c-154d52d1dab2.title: Bonafido
5a9ff2cd-84d6-41c5-bf6c-154d52d1dab2.text:
You've plenty of work to do, but you need a drink fast
- what do you go for?

76b6aa54-c49d-4b79-b5a7-ee1ceb5b5753.title: Bonafido
76b6aa54-c49d-4b79-b5a7-ee1ceb5b5753.text: What are you? A healthy builder? Of course, not juice!

c31be5c0-ace4-448a-9dbb-c1e509e7dc75.title: Bonafido
c31be5c0-ace4-448a-9dbb-c1e509e7dc75.text:
Ooh, get a load of the fancy pants here with her posh
wine! You're no builder.

options.text: Do a little dance and whistle as loud as you can

470df914-c03e-4057-ba74-2b1fe89cbb35.text: You do a little dance and whistle as loud as you can.

a68677f1-474d-49e6-b196-a9ef5eb094ca.title: Bonafido
a68677f1-474d-49e6-b196-a9ef5eb094ca.text: What on Gielinor are you doing? Get out of my sight.

ed88f2e2-2ede-4e82-ab56-bae1001f6054.title: Bonafido
ed88f2e2-2ede-4e82-ab56-bae1001f6054.text: You know, you have quite a talent there.

d5a252bf-0a20-4f4f-9b59-0c26186860ab.title: <player>
d5a252bf-0a20-4f4f-9b59-0c26186860ab.text:
Why thank you. Do you think I have what it takes to
become a famous whistler?

2c43e3da-a882-4bd3-a0bd-962dfc7df05a.title: Bonafido
2c43e3da-a882-4bd3-a0bd-962dfc7df05a.text:
What's a good sign that you need to replace your
trousers?

options.text: Your legs are getting a bit cold
They're ripped and full of holes
The colour is starting to fade

3cfcd4ea-4faa-4fde-9370-1da16b125e6a.title: <player>
3cfcd4ea-4faa-4fde-9370-1da16b125e6a.text: They're ripped and full of holes.

9dec665d-abe3-4eba-8efa-fafd67259a62.title: Bonafido
9dec665d-abe3-4eba-8efa-fafd67259a62.text: No, no, no. That's the only way they should be!

78e33943-1cbe-4b50-afcf-90a2045c4201.title: <player>
78e33943-1cbe-4b50-afcf-90a2045c4201.text: The colour is starting to fade?

a4fbba2c-dc7b-43d4-9936-93c971854bd2.title: Bonafido
a4fbba2c-dc7b-43d4-9936-93c971854bd2.text:
Oh no, you're really not getting the hang of this are
you?

dac85e47-f40f-4249-8c03-998f2d8ec1e9.title: <player>
dac85e47-f40f-4249-8c03-998f2d8ec1e9.text: Your legs are getting a bit cold?

5b612c16-553b-4011-8d9e-3ba3088c71dd.title: Bonafido
5b612c16-553b-4011-8d9e-3ba3088c71dd.text:
Exactamondo! Glad to see you are thinking like a
builder.

a7253ccc-4881-4104-be66-a9e386598cbd.title: Bonafido
a7253ccc-4881-4104-be66-a9e386598cbd.text:
Yes, obviously if your legs are cold, you lost your
trousers altogether!

1742cfda-a391-4f5a-b674-972a0847b558.title: <player>
1742cfda-a391-4f5a-b674-972a0847b558.text: That's just what I was thinking.

d06e0c67-6663-4f5e-b07b-90c383af4469.title: Bonafido
d06e0c67-6663-4f5e-b07b-90c383af4469.text:
Now the last question - what do you do if you cut
your finger?

07d8a214-1a24-4f04-8965-9a54257a7d42.title: Bonafido
07d8a214-1a24-4f04-8965-9a54257a7d42.text: When was the last time you saw a builder cry?

f5659552-65a6-4acf-b398-f48725382407.title: Bonafido
f5659552-65a6-4acf-b398-f48725382407.text:
Look, <player>, let me give you a bit of advice. If you
want to look weak, that's the best way to go.

51db2a6e-7634-44f1-b391-f5f59d66b705.title: <player>
51db2a6e-7634-44f1-b391-f5f59d66b705.text:
I suppose if it got infected, that'd just impress the crew
all the more.

f45ef405-a363-41f2-ad59-64ba20aba54b.title: Bonafido
f45ef405-a363-41f2-ad59-64ba20aba54b.text: Exactly, you're gettin the hang of this quickly!

918f5218-cdd6-4d67-b71f-631ee4d8b584.title: Bonafido
918f5218-cdd6-4d67-b71f-631ee4d8b584.text:
Cosmic! I canna see no reason why ya can't go in
t'tower now. But be careful, there be some precarious
situations in there.

cbb51b54-8f13-4f5a-a58e-700d44497be5.title: Bonafido
cbb51b54-8f13-4f5a-a58e-700d44497be5.text:
Well, there's a pipe system, a pressure machine and a
strange cage up at the top that needs finishing off. The
alchemists couldn't explain what they were for.

004df0a0-bd8a-463a-ab32-17652975e10b.title: Bonafido
004df0a0-bd8a-463a-ab32-17652975e10b.text: Hi, '<player> the Builder'! Been into the tower yet?

d354d4b9-8362-45b0-ac6e-0507c082b122.title: <player>
d354d4b9-8362-45b0-ac6e-0507c082b122.text:
Not yet, I'll go when I'm ready. I'm taking my time,
may have a quick cup of tea first.

923e387a-b3e1-4d61-9cbb-8bcbd7c1e8cc.title: <player>
923e387a-b3e1-4d61-9cbb-8bcbd7c1e8cc.text:
Heya, Bona. I had a look at the building. There's some
complex machinery in there! Going to cost someone.

fa3a2d1a-0e8c-42b3-b7c0-fb4fea579bea.title: Bonafido
fa3a2d1a-0e8c-42b3-b7c0-fb4fea579bea.text:
Yep, told ya so. Any idea what those alchemists are up
ta?

f32c4a88-64e6-4716-95fe-9e54d3501633.title: <player>
f32c4a88-64e6-4716-95fe-9e54d3501633.text:
Well, I agree now they're up to something. The
question is what...? I don't think we're going to find out
much from the alchmists, though.

02a9b7c8-cbe5-48a8-9ca9-13533cb9b96b.title: Bonafido
02a9b7c8-cbe5-48a8-9ca9-13533cb9b96b.text: So what are you going to do?

aba184a0-1085-4555-a56e-d4e0f45729c8.title: <player>
aba184a0-1085-4555-a56e-d4e0f45729c8.text:
I shall see if I can't fix it up and see for myself what is
going on. Should be able to get a good reward from
them. But don't worry, I'll make sure your efforts
don't go unpaid.

c602f456-0a04-4789-a576-440186642156.title: Bonafido
c602f456-0a04-4789-a576-440186642156.text: You're a star among builders, that ya are!

fb856169-c96e-41a7-980b-121e4b61c925.title: <player>
fb856169-c96e-41a7-980b-121e4b61c925.text: I'm really getting annoyed with those alchemists.

602267ae-2105-448b-ac4e-5ed27728fc96.title: <player>
602267ae-2105-448b-ac4e-5ed27728fc96.text:
Well, I completed the tower and I still have no idea
what it does, and then as soon as I tell Effigy of my
hard work, he doesn't say one word of thanks and legs
it off into the tower!

e4e56c80-a9aa-4e10-8424-024524771e04.title: Bonafido
e4e56c80-a9aa-4e10-8424-024524771e04.text:
Well, I'll be a rabbit in da eyes of a fox! Best ya chase
after 'im then and get us our dosh! Don't you do a
runner, now!

638878cf-3920-4038-8ac9-d8a592295017.title: <player>
638878cf-3920-4038-8ac9-d8a592295017.text:
Don't worry, I'm not about to let Effigy get away with
treating us builders like this!

ff498a10-f102-4d2d-8bfb-d87add4177ab.title: <player>
ff498a10-f102-4d2d-8bfb-d87add4177ab.text: You won't BELIEVE what I just saw!

563d8455-1e4e-41ce-ad30-2933d4be863b.title: <player>
563d8455-1e4e-41ce-ad30-2933d4be863b.text:
That tower is... a tower of life! I just witnessed with my
very own eyes the creation of an homunculus!

aa922642-cd6e-4b51-9927-c8d7e59e3255.title: <player>
aa922642-cd6e-4b51-9927-c8d7e59e3255.text:
Homunculus! They have found a way of creating life
itself, but the creature they have made is not a happy
being.

3fad71bb-3330-4dc1-abbb-ecfa930ab5f1.title: <player>
3fad71bb-3330-4dc1-abbb-ecfa930ab5f1.text:
Are you listening at all? This creature is very
dangerous, it needs to be stopped! And fast!

0f0ad18b-99a0-4959-9956-e6dd29a7121a.title: Bonafido
0f0ad18b-99a0-4959-9956-e6dd29a7121a.text: I'm glad you've got the money sorted.

718b5d57-eb85-4919-bed2-43e3176a5a3f.title: Bonafido
718b5d57-eb85-4919-bed2-43e3176a5a3f.text: Looks like we're out of a job then.

978c02f9-c230-4bd6-8b65-1f5377b8b00d.title: <player>
978c02f9-c230-4bd6-8b65-1f5377b8b00d.text:
Oh, I wouldn't worry about it. There are frequently
new buildings required around Gielinor. I'm sure your
services will be called upon again.

0d44f9b1-a2d3-406f-84da-fab46f050bb7.title: <player>
0d44f9b1-a2d3-406f-84da-fab46f050bb7.text: You still hangin' around the tower?

00e95e3c-d25a-42b6-aa61-7edeabeeaa3c.title: Bonafido
00e95e3c-d25a-42b6-aa61-7edeabeeaa3c.text:
Yeah, we need another job. But til then, we figured we
may as well wait ta see what else would turns up.
